movie.title: Battle of Britain
movie.plot: In 1940, the Royal Air Force fights a desperate battle against the might of the Luftwaffe for control of the skies over Britain, thus preventing the Nazi invasion of Britain.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 BAFTA Film Award. Another 1 win.
